node.text: Happy Birthday to me 🎉😆😆😆! It has reached a point where I’ve stopped keeping track of my age. I just know that I’m twenty-something 👻. No fancy restaurant or dinner but I am safe with my family and that’s good enough. Thank you to all who wished me and special thanks to sis for arranging all of these in quarantine - was shooketh when I came out of my room 🤡🤡🤡.
@rony_only Happy Birthday to You 🎊🎉 Stay Healthy and Safe 💖🎂🍾
Happy birthday 🎂 🎉 u have reached a point where i cannot call u xiao xian rou ald 🤭🤭
Happy bday🤩🎂! Wish u huat huat all the way 😁 and health n career level 🆙️!!
